data.description: Charming single level in Mint Valley neighborhood, in need of TLC. Functional floor plan with 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. The living room features vaulted ceilings and rustic wood beams. Cozy kitchen opens to dining area with fireplace and slider to back patio. Lovely backyard with raised garden beds and patio. Rotary Park is less than a block away!
